Interface NetworkInterfaceBase

  • All Superinterfaces:
    HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network.implementation.NetworkInterfaceInner>, HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network.implementation.NetworkManager>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    NetworkInterface, VirtualMachineScaleSetNetworkInterface

    public interface NetworkInterfaceBase
extends HasManager<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network.implementation.NetworkManager>, HasInner<com.microsoft.azure.v2.management.network.implementation.NetworkInterfaceInner>
    The base network interface shared across regular and virtual machine scale set network interface.
